{"tid":532571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【共享中國人榮耀】泰女幫襯夜市貴成倍 老闆：以為佢係中國人","createTime":"2018-01-18T03:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T08:45:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0daa3f0a6932d2b40dde067c5cfd83a6a0573b","tid":532571,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180118/large/1516243122_1321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180118%2Flarge%2F1516243122_1321.jpg&h=f4fa18e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人到外地旅遊，常被人視為土豪，最終消費時被當成「羊牯」。泰國一名女子到曼谷知名夜市TALAD NEON用餐，原本80泰銖（約20港元）的食物，老闆竟收她150泰銖（約37港元），原因竟然是「以為她是中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國當地媒體《khaosod》報道，泰國一女網友在fb發文，指自己日前到夜市用餐，點了一份雞蛋脆皮豬肉配羅勒葉，被收了150泰銖，讓她覺得太貴，因為同樣的食物在其他夜市只約60到70泰銖（15至17港元）。由於夜市有許多遊客，女網民特意問老闆是不是給泰國人的價錢，老闆卻回應是泰國人的價格。<br />\n<br />\n帖文後來引起熱議，而泰國傳媒隨後前往夜市，聯絡該名老闆娘，老闆娘指夜市有9成都是中國遊客，「還以為她是中國人」，並表示如果是泰國人的話，會收80泰銖價格。<br />\n<br />\n過去亦曾發生中國人在外地被「屈錢」例子，泰國《星暹日報》報道，此前有中國遊客在蘇梅島玩水上電單車後，檔主以一道刮痕為由，提出8萬泰銖（約1.96萬港元）的賠償，經協商，游客最後交了3萬泰銖（約7,400港元）才得以離開。"},{"pid":"4dfafd46d36fc7433830bb57de1d320c92b1c1d7","tid":532571,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180118/57721720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57721720&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8b310396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57721720&h=210bee0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180118/57721720</a>"},{"pid":"647ac4ff9cbe2ae3080721611981056a4528e92a","tid":532571,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24ab4bda9a88b1a9652aa0325dd02efdf82f9607","tid":532571,"uid":39800,"like":6,"dislike":78,"score":-72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"好彩我地係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d6249b366892ceb1272488465d0897962f9b08","tid":532571,"uid":35430,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"孽報報埋泰國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華人樣真係一種詛咒"},{"pid":"69bcca70ce714e45ad233030e32a9048e2942aae","tid":532571,"uid":38671,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c1d6249b366892ceb1272488465d0897962f9b08","tid":532571,"uid":35430,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"孽報報埋泰國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華人樣真係一種詛咒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"遲早排華全部亞洲人都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eb9f85ab9cef625f9fa1db0bdbe8934a501d18","tid":532571,"uid":113626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"果碟野係香港最少50$ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026f8667c22f9a2158b966de7c750c161d209931","tid":532571,"uid":41317,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"早輪有個旅遊post仲笑鳩香港人去泰國殺價cheap到死<br />\n邊個係豬兜都未清楚"},{"pid":"ecc1571298ab888a70ab4a26a3b2a05cccdc49c6","tid":532571,"uid":39706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"喺外國人眼中原來中國人係肥大嘅水魚.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b18d85c890c649a5a3f5872d6a39f76ad47d976","tid":532571,"uid":38671,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ecc1571298ab888a70ab4a26a3b2a05cccdc49c6","tid":532571,"uid":39706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:03:3